{"article_id":"FomiEcmU8k9qLeGL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The FBI gets a `` large volume '' of calls","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"after releasing photos of suspects ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"official says","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"`` Somebody out there knows '' the 2 suspects in the case ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"an FBI agent says","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The 2 men walked away from the scene `` pretty casually , ''","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"a federal official says","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"At an interfaith service , Obama tells Boston attackers :","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"`` We will find you ''","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"After three days of poring over photos and video ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"investigators appealed to the public to help them identify two men","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"now considered suspects in the Boston Marathon bombings .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"The men were photographed walking down Boylston Street , one behind the other , near the finish line of Monday 's race .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Suspect 1 was seen wearing a light-colored , collarless shirt underneath a dark-colored jacket and wearing a dark baseball cap .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"The man","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"identified as Suspect 2","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"was seen setting down a backpack at the site of the second explosion `` within minutes '' of the blasts","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"that killed three people","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"and wounded nearly 180 ,","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"said Special Agent Rick DesLauriers , the head of the FBI 's Boston office .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"He was wearing a light-colored hooded sweatshirt , a black jacket and a white baseball cap","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"turned backward .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"In particular , DesLauriers asked for help from anyone","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"standing in front of the Forum restaurant ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"where the second bombing happened .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"`` Somebody out there knows these individuals as friends , neighbors , co-workers or family members of the suspects , ''","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"DesLauriers said .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"`` And","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"though it may be difficult ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"the nation is counting on those with information to come forward","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"and provide it to us . ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"How FBI zeroed in on bombing suspects","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"How FBI zeroed in on bombing suspects","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"03:21","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Source :","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Suspects stayed","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"to watch carnage","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Source :","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Suspects stayed to watch carnage","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"01:17","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"FBI releases photos , video of suspects","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"FBI releases photos , video of suspects","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"02:46","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Mailbox might have saved this man 's life","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Mailbox might have saved this man 's life","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"03:13","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"People with possible information on the two men were urged to go to the FBI 's website , https : //bostonmarathontips.fbi.gov ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"or call 800-CALL-FBI","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"( 800-225-5324 ) .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"By Thursday evening , authorities already had received a `` large volume of calls ...","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"as a result of the photos , ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"an FBI official said .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"The FBI 's website , moreover , had been inundated with record traffic .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"It was n't immediately known then","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"whether any of the tips had led to the suspects .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"DesLauriers cautioned","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that anyone","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"who think","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"they know their identities","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"should be careful ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and consider them","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"armed and `` extremely dangerous . ''","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"`` No one should approach them , ''","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"`` No one should attempt to apprehend them except law enforcement . ''","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Other footage , still unreleased , shows","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"that the two suspects stayed at the scene","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"to watch the carnage unfold ,","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"a federal law enforcement official with knowledge of the investigation told CNN 's Susan Candiotti .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"`` When the bombs blow up ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"when most people are running away","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"and victims were lying on the ground ,","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"the two suspects walk away pretty casually , ''","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"said the official ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"who has seen the unreleased video .","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"`` They acted differently than everyone else . ''","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"While video","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"of at least one suspect","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"planting the bomb","depth":16},{"id":92,"text":"exists ,","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"the FBI had chosen not to release it ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"according to the official .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"One reason ,","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"according to the official ,","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"is that","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"were the media to repeatedly show the suspects","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"leaving the bomb ,","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"it might cause some people to overreact","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"if they came into contact with them .","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"DesLauriers said","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"intelligence had been developed on the first suspect `` within the last day or so . ''","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"The official","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"who spoke with CNN","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"images of the second suspect were isolated Wednesday .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"The investigation also turned toward the possibility","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"that the bombs had been detonated by remote control ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"a federal law enforcement official","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"briefed on the investigation","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"said Thursday .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"Investigators contacted the maker of a battery","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"found in the debris of the blasts ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"said Benjamin Mull , a vice president at Tenergy Corporation .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"One of the firm 's batteries ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"typically used in remote-controlled hobby cars ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"was found in the aftermath of the attack ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"connected to some wires and a piece of plastic .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Examining photo evidence from bomb site","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"Examining photo evidence from bomb site","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"01:36","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Victim :","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"I saw things","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"I wish","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"I did n't see","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"Victim :","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"I saw things","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"I wish","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"I did n't see","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"06:09 JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Dodd :","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"' I saw humanity at its finest '","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"MUST WATCH Dodd :","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"' I saw humanity at its finest '","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"03:29","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"Picture shows suspicious bag at marathon","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"Picture shows suspicious bag at marathon 00:40","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"In the early hours of the investigation , a law enforcement official told CNN","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"that the bombs were probably detonated by timers .","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"The FBI has said","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"details of the detonating system were unknown .","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"While the latest clues moved the investigation forward ,","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"it is still unclear","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"whether the attack was an act of domestic or foreign terrorism .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"Thursday evening 's FBI announcement capped a day","depth":5},{"id":157,"text":"in which President Barack Obama brought a mixture of reassurance and defiance to an interfaith memorial service in the city 's Cathedral of the Holy Cross .","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"Whoever planted the bombs `` picked the wrong city ''","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"to attack ,","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"`` Every one of us stands with you , ''","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"Obama told the crowd .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"`` Boston may be your hometown","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"-- but we claim it , too . ...","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"For millions of us , what happened on Monday is personal . ''","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"Addressing the still-unknown perpetrators ,","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"Obama added :","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"`` Yes , we will find you .","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"And yes , you will face justice .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"We will hold you accountable . ''","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"And he looked ahead to next year 's race ,","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"predicting","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"that `` the world will return to this great American city","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"to run even harder","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"and to cheer even louder for the 118th Boston Marathon .","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"Bet on it . ''","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"Among the crowd of about 2,000 were first lady Michelle Obama ; the president 's Republican challenger last November , former Massachusetts Gov . Mitt Romney ; the state 's current governor , Deval Patrick ; and Boston Mayor Thomas Menino .","depth":5},{"id":178,"text":"During an interlude , attendees were soothed by a performance by famed cellist Yo-Yo Ma .","depth":6},{"id":179,"text":"Menino praised each of the three bystanders","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"who were killed in the blasts","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"-- Martin Richard ,","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"described as a `` young boy with a big heart '' ;","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"Krystle Campbell ,","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"whose spirit `` brought her to the marathon year after year '' ;","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"and Lingzu Lu ,","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"who `` came to the city in search of an education . ''","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"The audience also included scores of police officers and other first responders .","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"Crowds erupted in cheers","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"as the cathedral emptied out at the end of the service ,","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"while others sang the national anthem .","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"Obama also stopped at a high school","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"to thank a group of first responders and volunteers","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"and met with patients","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"recovering from the attacks at Massachusetts General Hospital .","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"`` It was extremely uplifting for them , ''","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"said Dr. David King , a trauma surgeon at the hospital .","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"it 's incredibly inspiring that he would take time out","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"and visit them","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"and have a sincere interaction with all of these folks","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"that have been hurt . ''","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"Obama `` was humbled by the patients ' bravery and their fortitude and their drive","depth":13},{"id":203,"text":"to continue , ''","depth":13},{"id":204,"text":"he added .","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"The first lady met with patients , families and hospital staff at Boston Children 's Hospital and Brigham and Women 's Hospital ,","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"the White House said .","depth":9},{"id":207,"text":"Investigators say","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"the bombs ,","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"which exploded 12 seconds apart ,","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"were designed","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"to deliver the most vicious suffering .","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"A total of 59 people remained hospitalized on Thursday , six of them in critical condition ,","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"according to Boston-area hospitals .","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"At least 13 people lost limbs","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"as a result of the bombing .","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"One device was housed in a pressure cooker","depth":14},{"id":217,"text":"hidden inside a backpack ,","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"the FBI said .","depth":13},{"id":219,"text":"The device also had fragments","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"that may have included nails , BBs and ball bearings ,","depth":14},{"id":221,"text":"the agency said .","depth":13},{"id":222,"text":"The second bomb was in a metal container ,","depth":13},{"id":223,"text":"but it was unclear whether it was in a pressure cooker as well ,","depth":13},{"id":224,"text":"the FBI said .","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"Photos","depth":14},{"id":226,"text":"obtained by CNN","depth":14},{"id":227,"text":"show the remains of a pressure cooker","depth":14},{"id":228,"text":"found at the scene ,","depth":14},{"id":229,"text":"along with a shredded black backpack and what appear to be metal pellets or ball bearings .","depth":12},{"id":230,"text":"They were sent to the FBI 's national laboratory in Virginia ,","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"where technicians will try to reconstruct the devices .","depth":12},{"id":232,"text":"In the past , the U.S. government has warned federal agencies","depth":8},{"id":233,"text":"that terrorists could turn pressure cookers into bombs","depth":9},{"id":234,"text":"by packing them with explosives and shrapnel","depth":10},{"id":235,"text":"and detonating them with blasting caps .","depth":10},{"id":236,"text":"Richard , the 8-year-old boy with a gap-tooth grin and bright eyes .","depth":8},{"id":237,"text":"He loved to run and play in his yard .","depth":8},{"id":238,"text":"Campbell , a 29-year-old freckle-faced woman","depth":10},{"id":239,"text":"described by her mother as having `` a heart of gold . '' Lu , the Chinese graduate student at Boston University","depth":10},{"id":240,"text":"who had moved to the city last fall ,","depth":9},{"id":241,"text":"making friends","depth":9},{"id":242,"text":"and soaking up new experiences .","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"The U.S. State Department has been in contact with her family and the Chinese Foreign Ministry ,","depth":7},{"id":244,"text":"Secretary of State John Kerry said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":245,"text":"released Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":246,"text":"`` We stand ready to provide whatever appropriate assistance","depth":9},{"id":247,"text":"we can","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"to the family members of foreign nationals in the aftermath of this despicable act of terror , ''","depth":8},{"id":249,"text":"Kerry said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":499,"left":0,"right":498,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":498,"left":404,"right":497,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":404,"left":258,"right":403,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":258,"left":252,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":251,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":253,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":254,"right":255,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":403,"left":306,"right":402,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":306,"left":279,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent